First Uranium Says Mining Operations Resume at Ezulwini Following Fatality

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-03-18T06:54:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-18/first-uranium-says-mining-operations-resume-at-ezulwini-following-fatality.html
  First Uranium Corp. (FIU)  said all mining
operations, with the exception of the board and pillar section
where a fatal accident occurred, resumed with the night shift on
March 17.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
